  "text": "6 Ordinance 2 (II) POWERS AND PRIVILEGES OF THE DEANS OF FACULTIES 1. The Dean of the Faculty shall: (1) 'be entitled to such allowances and amenities as the Majlis-i- Muntazimah (Executive Council) may approve from time to time; (2) operate the Budget of the Faculty; (3) be responsible for the records, furniture and equipment under him; (4) be empowered to remove the name from the rolls and readmit a student in the Faculty concerned; (5) be empowered to withhold the Hall Ticket of student of the Faculty for valid reasons; and (6) exercise such other powers and perfom such other functions, as may be delegated or assigned to him by the Shaikhul Jamia (Vice- Chancellor) or the Majlis-i- Muntazimah (Executive Council). -- 1 of 1 --",
